# Baseline Algorithm Stack

Implement under `src/fedmaq/baselines/` and track in `.cursor/project/baseline_registry.md`:

| Group | Algorithms |
| ----- | ---------- |
| Vanilla floor | FedAvg, FedProx |
| Static compression | DAdaQuant, FedPAQ |
| Pure KD ablation | FedKD, FedDistill |
| Adaptive / bandwidth-aware | AdaGQ, LAQ-HC |
| Quantization + KD (SOTA targets) | DynFed, AdaDQ-KD, FedDT |

Update `baseline_registry.md` when adding or porting a baseline.
